Nigerian singer, Seyi Shay has announced her engagement. Seyi Shay made this known in a recent interview with Beat Fm. Flaunting her ring, the singer confirmed she said yes to a man who promised to marry her. She, however, failed to reveal the identity of the man. The interviewer asked “Is that ring an engagement?” Responding, Seyi Shay said, “Yes, I am engaged, some guy gave it to me and would marry me. “It’s a diamond ring for real and it’s forever. “I was already glowing before I met him, if I was not a package, I wouldn’t have said yes.”